<h1>Siam-is18 Registration</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>Registration Fees</h2>
    <%= render 'payments/list' %>  
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>Your data</h2>
    <%= render current_user %>  
    <%= link_to_edit 'modify', edit_user_path(current_user) %>  
  </div>
</div>

<p>If you do not join SIAM before you register, SIAM allows attendees who pay the non-member rate to apply the difference between it and the member rate toward buying an individual membership.  We will continue to offer this option and expand the offer to those who pay the non-member minisymposia organizer or speaker rate. </p>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>Conference Registration Fee Includes:</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Admission to all technical sessions</li>
      <li>Business Meeting (open to SIAG/IS members)</li>
      <li>Coffee breaks daily</li>
      <li>Room set-ups and audio/visual equipment</li>
      <li>Welcome Reception and Poster Session</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <p class="centered">
    <% if current_user.can_register? %>  
      <%= link_to new_payment_path, class: "big_pay_button" do %>  
        PAY <strong><%= @price_to_pay_and_reason[0] %> &euro;</strong> for Registration
        <br/>(<%= @price_to_pay_and_reason[1] %>)
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

